<script>
import axios from 'axios'
export default {
  name: 'App',
  methods: {
    async online() {
            try {
                let response = await axios.get(`https://phplaravel-729699-3062059.cloudwaysapps.com/api/v1/ping`, {});
                console.info("Pong")
                console.log(response);
            } catch (error) {
                console.warn("Not online", error)
            }
        },
  },
  mounted (){
    this.online();
  }
}
</script>
